725577f-c.title: Queens: 67th Street - Maurice Avenue
725577f-c.text:
67t) Street, east side, between Maurice and Garfield Aves., showing in a set of three views the R. Douglas house from 1873 to 1891. A
cigar manufacturer was the occupant in 1924.
January 1924.
Views 1 & 2.
View 3: February 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
